item.title: New Village Needs People!
item.content:encoded:
I've been a long time Billy player and now I've taken the plunge into Kageship! Please come and join this new and exciting village!
Starting out small but I plan to grow quickly.
Please join Data Village, the Village hidden in the Matrix.
